  <p align="left"><strong><font size="+1">2009 Dates</font></strong><br>
    <br>
    Confirming dates and details for key Incedo events next year:<br>
    <br>
    1. <strong>Young Leaders Weekend</strong> - February 6-8 Christchurch.<br>
    The MLT will contact those they are inviting to this, individually.<br>
    <br>
    2. <strong>Surge</strong> - April 15-18 in Whangarei<br>
    (middle weekend of the school holidays)<br>
    <br>
    3. <strong>Youth Worker Training</strong><br>
    Mike Garland and Darryl Gardiner will be running two Youth Worker training weekends.<br>
    South Island - June 27-28 Christchurch<br>
    North Island - August 22-23 Taupo or Palmerston North<br>
    This is highly recommended for Incedo members and helpers<br>
    <br>
    4. <strong>Road Show</strong><br>
    We are organizing a 10-day Road Show over two weekends, visitng 3-4 Incedo bases, featuring a provocative range of speakers. The goal is to connect with Christians looking to get on the missional edge. <br>
    We are still finalizing dates but it will be in the June-August period.<br>
    <br>
    5. <strong>The Gathering</strong> - September 25-27 Nelson<br>
    (First weekend of school holidays)</p>
  <p align="left"> Please write these into your planning for 2009, now, so that you don't clash with local events.</p>
  <p align="left">Surge and The Gathering are compulsory for Incedo members.<br>
        <br>
